  "prompt": "What is that you have learnt from Quora?",
  "response": "As an AI, I don't learn or extract information from external sources like Quora in real-time. Instead, I have been trained on a diverse range of data, including texts from books, articles, and websites available up until October 2021. This means I can provide information and answer questions based on that training, but I don't have the ability to browse the web or access Quora or any other site for new information. If you have specific questions or topics related to what is commonly discussed on Quora, feel free to ask!",
